1 commits unlawful entry by a serious sex offender, a Level 6 felony.
2 (c) It is a defense to a prosecution under subsection (b) that:
3 (1) a religious institution or house of worship is located on the
4 school property; and
5 (2) the person:
6 (A) enters the school property or other entity described in
