COMMITTEE REPORT
Mr. President: The Senate Committee on Corrections and Criminal
Law, to which was referred Senate Bill No. 119, has had the same
under consideration and begs leave to report the same back to the
Senate with the recommendation that said bill be AMENDED as
follows:
Page 2, line 31, delete "who:" and insert "who knowingly or
intentionally:".
Page 2, line 32, strike "knowingly or intentionally".
Page 2, line 39, delete "unlawful".
and when so amended that said bill do pass.
(Reference is to SB 119 as introduced.)
FREEMAN, Chairperson
Committee Vote: Yeas 8, Nays 0.
